1
00:00:11,820 --> 00:00:14,060
[Kim Hyeonseo as Sung Ho]

2
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:17,120
[Jung Myeongcheol as Yoo Sehyun]

3
00:00:17,340 --> 00:00:19,580
[Kim Seonghyuk as Kwon Hyukjae]

4
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:22,500
[Jung Hyunwoong as Kim Minho]

5
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:37,000
[Sin and Love]

6
00:00:37,860 --> 00:00:39,820
[Episode 5]

7
00:01:21,570 --> 00:01:23,250
What's up with everyone?

8
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:26,950
Why's Sung Ho defending Yoo Sehyun again?

9
00:01:35,550 --> 00:01:37,300
Damn it.

10
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,650
Are you okay?

11
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:57,009
I don't understand.

12
00:01:58,650 --> 00:02:00,480
Why's Sung Ho and Yoo Sehyun...

13
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,300
Is that important?

14
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,100
I want to ruin both of them.

15
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,490
Don't let your emotions drive you.

16
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:35,710
Your mouth.

17
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,210
It hurts, right?

18
00:02:51,940 --> 00:02:52,980
No.

19
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:05,150
What are we doing next?

20
00:03:07,660 --> 00:03:08,660
Don't be anxious.

21
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:18,650
Show me

22
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:22,010
how loyal you are.

23
00:05:19,470 --> 00:05:20,080
Get in.

24
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,060
Are you okay?

25
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:45,950
I'm fine.

26
00:05:50,690 --> 00:05:51,780
Liar.

27
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:54,260
Is it obvious?

28
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:56,150
Yeah.

29
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:06,520
I told you not to come to me.

30
00:06:09,110 --> 00:06:10,610
When did I go to you?

31
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:12,810
You were the one who came to me.

32
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:25,380
Let's go home.

33
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:06,510
Let's go.

34
00:08:13,210 --> 00:08:14,310
Hold still.

35
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,100
Why are you suffering alone?

36
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:17,840
Done.

37
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:22,180
Why'd it take so long?

38
00:09:24,410 --> 00:09:25,350
Because I can.

39
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:31,650
You...

40
00:09:33,060 --> 00:09:34,150
What are you thinking

41
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,480
while seeing me in pain?

42
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,520
Do you think I'm you?

43
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,110
Don't just look at my wound.

44
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:49,050
Look here too.

45
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:51,810
I'm hurt here too.

46
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,080
Looks fine to me.

47
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,140
If you treat my wounds

48
00:10:04,350 --> 00:10:05,580
every time I get hurt,

49
00:10:06,850 --> 00:10:09,050
I'd be happy to get hurt a million times.

50
00:10:10,730 --> 00:10:12,050
Don't be silly.

51
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:17,850
Sung Ho.

52
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:21,980
I'm sorry.

53
00:10:23,310 --> 00:10:24,770
As long as you're willing,

54
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,830
I'll always be by your side.

55
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:15,750
So it's your first time.

56
00:11:17,770 --> 00:11:18,610
Are you okay?

57
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,350
What should we do next?

58
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:30,030
Is there a mission?

59
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:40,080
Drink the milk first.

60
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:26,020
You're awake.

61
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,740
Did you sleep well?

62
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:31,580
Yeah.

63
00:12:32,650 --> 00:12:34,710
I haven't slept so well in a long time.

64
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:37,210
You can sleep more.

65
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,360
Okay.

66
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:00,240
It's Kwon Hyukjae.

67
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:02,340
Answer it.

68
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,180
Yes, Officer Kwon.

69
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,910
Good job.

70
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,760
Sung Ho's into you again.

71
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,110
Next up,

72
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:28,750
the files I want:

73
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,150
the ledger and drug records.

74
00:13:32,650 --> 00:13:34,710
Once I get them, I'll keep my promise.

75
00:13:35,190 --> 00:13:36,710
You'll be reinstated to the force

76
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:38,710
and get the 500 billion won you want.

77
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:39,710
But...

78
00:13:41,410 --> 00:13:42,610
don't make mistakes.

79
00:13:43,050 --> 00:13:44,710
I'm watching your every move.

80
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:47,310
I can even hear your breathing.

81
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,350
If you lie to me,

82
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:51,850
I'll make your life miserable.

83
00:13:58,340 --> 00:13:59,810
He said he's watching us.

84
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:03,250
I know.

85
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:07,000
That's why we need to be more cautious.

86
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:11,250
Let's be brave.

87
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:15,270
Kwon Hyukjae thinks

88
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,870
we'll make a move right away.

89
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:20,370
So we need to keep a low profile

90
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:23,210
and gather evidence of his crimes.

91
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:29,780
Sung Ho,

92
00:14:30,810 --> 00:14:31,740
that mission...

93
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:36,650
Tell me.

94
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:38,810
What is the crux?

95
00:14:40,990 --> 00:14:42,600
It's harder than I thought.

96
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:46,480
There's everything in Gangnam Palace:

97
00:14:47,330 --> 00:14:48,190
prostitution,

98
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:49,510
drugs,

99
00:14:50,250 --> 00:14:50,850
gambling.

100
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:55,880
Do as he says for tomorrow.

101
00:14:57,690 --> 00:14:59,300
Record everything you do.

102
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,810
Drugs, prostitution, gambling—

103
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:04,470
make a backup for everything.

104
00:15:07,450 --> 00:15:08,180
Okay.

105
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:51,700
[Internal Inspection Bureau,
National Police Agency, Republic of Korea]

106
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,700
[Internal Confidential Dossier]

107
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:00,000
[Misconduct and involvement
in criminal activities]

108
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,560
[14 Mar 2023: Took a bribe of 50 million
from the CEO of Luce Club in Gangnam]

109
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:02,980
[Deleted the list of drug users
who are Club VIPs;
Deleted CCTV server]

110
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:16,980
This time,

111
00:16:18,180 --> 00:16:19,380
I'll do as you say.

112
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:11,460
[Kwon Hyukjae's
Visiting Records and Financial Files]

113
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,550
[17 Mar 2020: Yongsan, Mr. V,
50 million won, drug envelope]

114
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,099
[22 Jul 2020: Gangnam, Mr. Choi,
120 million won, sexual bribery]

115
00:17:18,099 --> 00:17:19,300
[11 Feb 2021: Incheon, Mr. J,
$3000, mail, first test on Telegram]

116
00:17:41,220 --> 00:17:43,020
I'm sorry for leaving you alone.

117
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,020
It's been a long wait.

118
00:17:53,560 --> 00:17:54,310
I know.

119
00:18:06,210 --> 00:18:06,880
I'm sorry.

120
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:09,840
For what?

121
00:18:11,370 --> 00:18:12,370
For running away.

122
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:20,030
Trust me one more time.

123
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,130
I've waited for so long.

124
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:53,910
I've been suppressing my urges.

125
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:36,280
I've waited for so long.

126
00:19:38,290 --> 00:19:39,420
Why did you run away?

127
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:48,390
Can I take off your clothes?

128
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:49,700
Yeah.

129
00:19:52,450 --> 00:19:53,850
When this case is over...

130
00:19:56,150 --> 00:19:57,380
let's go to the beach.

131
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,000
The beach?

132
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:04,780
Why?

133
00:20:07,050 --> 00:20:08,850
Haven't you always wanted to go?

134
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,760
Promise me.

135
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:41,960
[Sin and Love]
